# header-row-localization-and-mapping

**When to use**: Any spreadsheet task requiring column selection by header name, to guarantee correct operation especially when sheet structure changes.

**Why it works**: All rollouts succeeded because this technique reliably mapped both source and target fields even if sheet layout varied, preventing wrong-cell errors and supporting correct matching logic.

